postscript.p:
[On July 17 the Department sent to the British Embassy a statement of the
                        number of American civilians held in Japanese custody as of July 12, as
                        follows: Philippine Islands, 4768; China, 964; Japan, 173; Malaya, 35;
                        Manchuria, 9; Borneo, 9; Indochina, 8; Thailand, 7; Burma, 6; Sumatra, 3;
                        Korea, 1; and Formosa, 1.
